{
  "chapter": 8,
  "chapter_summary": "萧秋水路过长安谪仙楼，目睹幽州双鬼刁怡保、刁金保在酒楼闹事，终南剑派弟子原纹瘦与捕快牛送之出手均被打退。黑煞神蒲江沙闯入搅局，皇甫公子手下齐昨飞、黎九、潘桂现身平乱，以精湛武功制服众人，赢得长安百姓喝彩。萧秋水暗中跟踪齐昨飞三人至大雁塔，发现谪仙楼打斗竟是一场精心策划的假戏——七人齐聚密会，主持者为皇甫世家智囊\"九尾狐\"叠不叠。众人坦承一切是为了帮少主皇甫高桥扬名，助其在湖北\"神州结义\"盟主选拔中胜过萧秋水。萧秋水偷听被叠不叠发现，仓皇逃走时遗失了梵文真经，虽已远遁仍决定折返取回。本章揭示皇甫高桥阵营暗中操纵舆论的阴谋，也展现了萧秋水面对强敌时的自卑与释然。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_二掌柜",
      "speaker_name": "二掌柜",
      "listener": "char_刁怡保",
      "text": "大爷，两位大爷，小店是小本生意……求求你俩行行好事，约战摆在别处……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_刁金保",
      "speaker_name": "使方天戟的大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "住口！我们约定对方决战的地方，怎可以随随便便更改的！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "城里长辈",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不行呀。这里是有名之地，你俩看看，墙上还留有李白的题诗呢……不能在此决斗呀。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "围观百姓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在别人店里打杀，把人家楼店都砸了，叫人家吃什么来着……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "围观百姓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天哪…这个年头王法去了哪里？……天理何在呀！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_原纹瘦",
      "speaker_name": "原纹瘦",
      "listener": "char_刁怡保",
      "text": "吠！你们两个狗徒，在这里作威作福，目无王法么？！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_刁金保",
      "speaker_name": "使方天戟的大汉",
      "listener": "char_原纹瘦",
      "text": "你又是什么东西？！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_原纹瘦",
      "speaker_name": "原纹瘦",
      "listener": "char_刁金保",
      "text": "你有眼不识泰山，我是终南剑派第十一代弟子原纹瘦，他是我堂兄，长安名捕快'手到擒来'牛送之，你们还不走，就抓你们到衙府里去。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_原纹瘦",
      "speaker_name": "原纹瘦",
      "listener": "char_刁怡保",
      "text": "要你知道讪笑的代价。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_刁怡保",
      "speaker_name": "使拐子棍的大汉",
      "listener": "char_牛送之",
      "text": "这等三脚猫功夫，也来唬人。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_黑煞神",
      "speaker_name": "黑煞神",
      "listener": "char_刁怡保",
      "text": "喂，幽州双鬼，我黑煞神来了！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_黑煞神",
      "speaker_name": "黑煞神",
      "listener": "char_刁怡保",
      "text": "你们还不下来迎接！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_刁怡保",
      "speaker_name": "使拐子棍的大汉",
      "listener": "char_黑煞神",
      "text": "你自己上来呀。",
      "tone": "挑衅",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_刁金保",
      "speaker_name": "使方天戟的大汉",
      "listener": "char_黑煞神",
      "text": "这儿有人阻挡我们的比武哩！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_黑煞神",
      "speaker_name": "黑煞神",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？！是谁！好大的胆子！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_黑煞神",
      "speaker_name": "黑煞神",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是谁？！谁敢如此？！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_黑煞神",
      "speaker_name": "黑煞神",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们是么？！是不是你们？！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_黑煞神",
      "speaker_name": "黑煞神",
      "listener": "char_刁怡保",
      "text": "好了。这儿干干净净，正合我们决一死战。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "屏风后青年",
      "listener": "char_黑煞神",
      "text": "等一等。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_黑煞神",
      "speaker_name": "黑煞神",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是什么人？！不怕我黑煞神拔你的舌头吗？！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_齐昨飞",
      "speaker_name": "齐昨飞",
      "listener": "char_黑煞神",
      "text": "你听过皇甫公子未？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_黑煞神",
      "speaker_name": "黑煞神",
      "listener": "char_齐昨飞",
      "text": "皇甫公了……皇甫高桥是你什么人？！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长安民众甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "皇甫高桥……就是皇甫公子！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长安民众乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "皇甫公子行侠仗义，这次有他出来……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长安民众丙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一切问题可都解决！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长安民众丁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "皇甫公子的人，一定能好好教训这三个煞星！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_齐昨飞",
      "speaker_name": "齐昨飞",
      "listener": "长安民众",
      "text": "诸位放心，皇甫公子吩咐过，任何人敢欺压民众，我们都不会放过他！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "围观百姓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人就是皇甫公子的拜把弟兄，叫做齐咋飞，旁边的是皇甫公子近身护卫，一个叫做'竹竿'黎九，一个叫作'冬瓜'潘桂，三人武功都很高。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "围观百姓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唉，不知是不是那三个煞星的对手！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_黑煞神",
      "speaker_name": "黑煞神",
      "listener": "char_齐昨飞",
      "text": "喂，齐大管家的，我们三人没惹你，你也少来惹我！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_齐昨飞",
      "speaker_name": "齐昨飞",
      "listener": "char_黑煞神",
      "text": "滚出去！长安城岂是容你撒野之地？！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_黑煞神",
      "speaker_name": "黑煞神",
      "listener": "char_齐昨飞",
      "text": "我是给面子皇甫高桥！你小子不知好歹，我先宰了你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_黎九",
      "speaker_name": "黎九",
      "listener": "char_刁怡保",
      "text": "公子有令……放你们一条生路。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_潘桂",
      "speaker_name": "潘桂",
      "listener": "char_刁怡保",
      "text": "这是你们最后一次活命的机会了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_刁怡保",
      "speaker_name": "幽州二鬼",
      "listener": "char_齐昨飞",
      "text": "皇甫公子圣明，幽州二鬼得饶以不杀，日后必当报答，肝脑涂地，在所不辞。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长安民众",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！好！皇甫公子座下高手果然要得！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "谪仙楼伙计",
      "listener": "char_齐昨飞",
      "text": "这次幸得三位前来，否则小店不堪设想……",
      "tone": "感激",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "谪仙楼伙计",
      "listener": "char_齐昨飞",
      "text": "三位能不毁一椅一桌赶走三个凶徒，确是神乎其技……",
      "tone": "感激",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_齐昨飞",
      "speaker_name": "齐昨飞",
      "listener": "长安民众",
      "text": "我们只是作该作之事而已……这一切都是皇甫公子对我们耳提面命的……就连武功，也是皇甫公子亲传……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_萧秋水",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小心！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_叠不叠",
      "speaker_name": "叠不叠",
      "listener": "char_齐昨飞",
      "text": "辛苦你们了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_潘桂",
      "speaker_name": "潘桂",
      "listener": "char_叠不叠",
      "text": "应该的，为公子爷做这件事情，我们可心里服气。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_齐昨飞",
      "speaker_name": "齐昨飞",
      "listener": "char_黑煞神",
      "text": "……只不过下手重了些，要七阿哥吃亏了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_黑煞神",
      "speaker_name": "黑煞神",
      "listener": "char_齐昨飞",
      "text": "也没什么。那些是猪血，一路洒过去，倒吓着了行人。齐老大也是为了公子爷，我蒲江沙还有什么话说。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_刁金保",
      "speaker_name": "刁金保",
      "listener": "char_叠不叠",
      "text": "……七阿哥都不埋怨，我们刁家兄弟，吃的更是公子爷的饭，哪里有话好说的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_叠不叠",
      "speaker_name": "叠不叠",
      "listener": "char_齐昨飞",
      "text": "大家都是为了少君做事，甭客气——我们先后己用各种不同的方式，唱了许多出戏，只是少君不知道罢了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_刁怡保",
      "speaker_name": "刁怡保",
      "listener": "char_叠不叠",
      "text": "公子爷知道我们这么做，不知会不会怪罪我们呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_齐昨飞",
      "speaker_name": "齐昨飞",
      "listener": "char_刁怡保",
      "text": "哪会！他不知道不就得了？！我们这般都是为他好，他不像那萧秋水，凡事出来自己闯，公子爷智能天纵，但极少出外，多在大本营里运筹帷幄，所以名声可能反而不及现在到处打击权力帮的萧秋水，——我们这样做，正是为他的名声呀。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_刁金保",
      "speaker_name": "刁金保",
      "listener": "char_齐昨飞",
      "text": "可是公子爷若知道我们这样做，恐怕他会不高兴的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_叠不叠",
      "speaker_name": "叠不叠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "少主知道，的确会不悦。我们的做法，是为了少主能在湖北'神州结义'选拔中获盟主之位，光宗耀祖，重振门榻，击败萧秋水，建立实力，对抗权力帮与朱大天王，如此苦心，一旦他知道了，应不会怪责我们的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_黑煞神",
      "speaker_name": "黑煞神",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "希望如此就好了，免得我们做恶人做了那么多之后，到头来得不到公子爷的原谅。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_黎九",
      "speaker_name": "黎九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我服侍少主已一段日子，知道少主脾性，他视兄弟们如至亲，无论如何，他都不会因此而与大伙儿不睦的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_潘桂",
      "speaker_name": "潘桂",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们反正也没伤人嘛！客串一下，替少主打响名头，又有什么不好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_刁怡保",
      "speaker_name": "刁怡保",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "话虽那么讲，但公子爷的脾气……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_刁金保",
      "speaker_name": "刁金保",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哎，别管了，反正都作了嘛……让什么萧秋水的当盟主，我刁老二不服气，捧公子爷上来，总是应该；咱们公子爷可不是像人家靠运气乱闯出名堂的，咱……",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_齐昨飞",
      "speaker_name": "齐昨飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱公子爷是行大事不留名，十年如一日的哩……所以咱们就替他留留名！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_叠不叠",
      "speaker_name": "叠不叠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是谁？！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_潘桂",
      "speaker_name": "潘桂",
      "listener": "char_黎九",
      "text": "糟糕，给他听去了！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_黎九",
      "speaker_name": "黎九",
      "listener": "char_齐昨飞",
      "text": "那人似在茶楼上那人……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_齐昨飞",
      "speaker_name": "齐昨飞",
      "listener": "char_黎九",
      "text": "此人容貌，传说中与萧秋水酷似；如是他，给他听到了，传出去可糟透了！我轻功好，我去追他，你们守在这里！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_潘桂",
      "speaker_name": "潘桂",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "齐老大去追去了，他要我们留守。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_黎九",
      "speaker_name": "黎九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那人轻功好，只怕惟有齐老大和叠教师才追得上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_叠不叠",
      "speaker_name": "叠不叠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们进去塔里再说。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    }
  ],
